      "title": "Differential geometry of curves and surfaces",
      "abstract": "The goal of this article is to present the relation between some differential formulas, like the Gauss integral for a link, or the integral of the Gaussian curvature on a surface, and topological invariants like the linking number or the Euler characteristic."
